# Backend Tech Stack (`backend/`)

The `[backend/](mdc:common/backend)` directory houses the backend application.

-   It is an Express.js server.
-   It is built with Node.js and TypeScript.
-   Key configuration files (e.g., its own `[package.json](backend/package.json)`, `[tsconfig.json](backend/tsconfig.json)`) and the main entry point `[src/app.ts](backend/src/app.ts)` are located within this directory.
